description: The average time differences of high tide compared to Antwerp were digitized based on maps of the Tidal Book 2009. For the map these periods were converted to a time difference compared to Vlissingen.
keywords: getij, tijdsverschil, 2009, Antwerpen, Vlissingen, georefereren, vectoriseren, Tide, time difference, 2009, Antwerp, Vlissingen, Georeferencing, Vectoring, Hydrography
name: Average time differences between high tide in Antwerp and Vlissingen (Western Scheldt, 2009)
